name: Informants of the Osmerian Edge
description: Hailing from the searing apex of Mt. Kalfus, the Informants of the Osmerian Edge might haveâ€¦ killed their former house leader? And that worries some people? Maybe? Yikes. Stay away from these guys. One of the few who witnessed the Osmerian Anomaly, and equipped with the knowledge of what may have actually happened, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
